verbose_text: Since all of the known parn phenotypes are suppressed by loss-of-function mutations in AGS1 [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], we expected the parn-ags1 double mutants to reset their transcriptome to pre-starvation conditions just as readily as wildtype plants.
evidence: parn phenotypes are suppressed by loss-of-function mutations in AGS1
